# ax25d.conf changes for flexnetd with IW2OHX-3
#
# flexnetd binds IW2OHX-3 (the xnet port callsign) directly.
# This matches the ax1 interface address — no special kernel tricks needed.
#
# ENSURE [IW2OHX-3 VIA xnet] is NOT in ax25d.conf — flexnetd owns it.
#
# ax25d continues to own IW2OHX-7 on bpq and pcf for uronode.
#
# On the Xnet side, configure the FlexNet link to IW2OHX-3:
#   ro flexnet add xnet IW2OHX-3
